There are actually 3 types of accounts can be created
1) Business account => for company and person
2) Person account => for individual person
3) Group Household => for associating a group of members

a Person account can belong to only one household group but can be related to many household groups
Only person accounts can be added in household groups

Go to setup > custom settings > Wealth application configuration > enable rollups
to add a new life event > setup > object manager > person life events > event (picklist value) > add a new one

Person life events will be tied up to person accounts
Business milestones will be ties up to business accounts and household groups

